WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:06.000
Titanic departed with confidence, luxury, and the belief that technology had finally conquered the sea.

00:06.000 --> 00:12.000
But in the freezing darkness of the North Atlantic, a single collision changed everything.

00:12.000 --> 00:20.000
This story follows the hope, panic, and legacy of one of history's most famous maritime disasters.
